    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus containing around 20 species of aquatic plants found in shallow marshes, ponds, and streams, ranging from temperate to arctic regions. The plants provide food and cover for wildlife and waterfowl.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
